Compress Compressed EPWING CD-ROM Book
======================================

   `ebzip' can compress a CD-ROM book compressed with the EPWING
compression format.  It uncompress the book, and then recompresses the
book with the ebzip compression format.  Since the ebzip compression is
generally better than the EPWING compression format, the book
compressed by `ebzip' is smaller than original.


