Uncompress Compressed EPWING CD-ROM Book
========================================

   `ebzip' can uncompress a CD-ROM book compressed with the EPWING
compression format.  However, `ebzip' cannot restore the original
compressed book by compressing the uncompressed book again.  In other
words, `ebzip' support uncompression of the EPWING compression format,
but doesn't support compression.


